adminai@adminai-VirtualBox:/home$ type number
number is a function
number () 
{ 
    echo "Enter your number";
    read number;
    if (( number % 2 == 0)); then
        echo "Your number is even";
    else
        echo "Your number is odd";
    fi
}

adminai@adminai-VirtualBox:/home$ number
Enter your number
5
Your number is odd

